Cyber Claw:




Cyber Claw trod along, watching the surroundings carefully. It was 
her habit. She was always wary, and jumped at every shadow that could 
be Predacon. 

But now things could change. She would have to trust her own kind 
again. She may be nervous for a moment, but she had to fight it. 
There could be someone there to tell her to be calm.

She doubted that. It was rare when a Predacon care about the other. 

Cyber Claw stopped in her tracks. There was a figure, a gray and gold 
figure laying on the ground. She cocked her head and sniffed. It 
smelt familiar. She lowered her head and walked carefully towards it. 
It didn't move when she went closer to it. She soon found out that it 
was Rattrap. She noticed somethings different about it, but it was 
still that awful Maximal rodent. 

She flexed her sickle claws and gaped her mouth. She snarled at the 
damaged body. She spread her three digited fingers on her forepaws. 
She made her presence known to him, as a threat, and still nothing.

He was in stasis lock. 

She began to grin. She stood up tall and transformed to robot mode. 
She tapped him with the tip of her foot, with no reaction. She then 
picked him up. Using the rat could be useful as an acceptance for the 
Predacons. She took off in flight mode.
